data.description: Be sure to come and see this large 5BR/3.5BA Juniper Model home located in Collegiate Acres. With spacious bedrooms and lots of windows to let in the natural light, this home is sure to be a great place for any family. Large basement and rec-room offers a bedroom area with egress and a walk up basement. This home has additional features with the bumpouts, insta hot, deck and patio. Located with easy access to I-81 and many shopping amenities, this home is comfortable and convenient. Be sure to schedule your showing soon. Come enjoy this lovely home.
